Package entity

Class Project

java.lang.Object
entity.Project
public class Project extends Object
Models a BTO project managed within the system. Contains details such as available flats, pricing, associated manager, assigned officers, application period, and registration visibility.

      public Project(String projectName, String neighborhood, int availableTwoRoom, int sellingPriceTwoRoom, int availableThreeRoom, int sellingPriceThreeRoom, Date openingDate, Date closingDate, int maxOfficer)
      Creates a project with all relevant details and default visibility set to true.
      Parameters:
      projectName - the name of the project
      neighborhood - the neighborhood where the project is located
      availableTwoRoom - number of 2-room flats available
      sellingPriceTwoRoom - price for a 2-room flat
      availableThreeRoom - number of 3-room flats available
      sellingPriceThreeRoom - price for a 3-room flat
      openingDate - the application opening date
      closingDate - the application closing date
      maxOfficer - the number of officer slots available
